instructions: Put the Dinner Fork on the left of the Charger.
Put the Dinner Knife on the right of the Charger.
Put the salad fork on the left of the dinner fork
Put the Salad Knife on the right of the Dinner Knife.
Put the Soup Spoon on the right of the Salad Knife.
Put the Dessert Spoon above the Charger with the handle pointing to the right.
Put the Dessert Fork below the Dessert Spoon with the tines pointing to the right.
Put the Dinner Plate on top of the Charger.
Put the Bread Plate above the Dinner and Salad Forks.
Put the Butter Knife on the Bread Plate with the handle pointing to the 4:00 o'clock position.
Put the Water Glass above the two Dinner and Salad Knives.
